           <h4 class="widget-title widgettitle">
            Welcome
           </h4>
           <div class="textwidget">
            The Department of Sociology at Texas A&amp;M University offers a quality undergraduate education, recognized as one of the nation’s leading programs in the field by the American Sociological Association.
The department offers a broad-based curriculum with excellent opportunities for training in various areas of faculty expertise and research.
